{"tid":537600,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《逃生魔幻紀》《大娛樂家》成為美國聖誕檔期黑馬","createTime":"2018-01-23T00:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T15:12:50.000Z","uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"815228c741f6d361d1b2e23dcacd6443de45a93c","tid":537600,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T00:05:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boxofficemojo.com%2Fweekend%2Fchart%2F&d=5S%2FKjOyjpYfYwsgrUN5viEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6b5bd088\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/</a><br />\nJumanji 已經上映第五個星期仍然無懼所有新片穩守周末票房冠軍<br />\n已經超越Skyfall成為Sony發行電影之中(唔計蜘蛛俠)美國票房最高嘅電影<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/23/075255_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F23%2F075255_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=82cfc6a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大娛樂家開畫首個周末票房不足千萬美金<br />\n本來預計最終票房唔過五千萬<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekend&amp;id=greatestshowman.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boxofficemojo.com%2Fmovies%2F%3Fpage%3Dweekend%26id%3Dgreatestshowman.htm&d=5S%2FKjOyjpYfYwsgrUN5viEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=6aa8da40\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?page=weekend&amp;id=greatestshowman.htm</a><br />\n但係後勁瘋狂<br />\n之後每一個周末票房都維持係一千萬以上，有別於大部份電影頭一個周末收入最高嘅慣例<br />\n累積票房慢慢突破左一億向億五進發<br />\n呼應左電影入面大眾口碑比專業評價重要得多嘅主題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75c37c6faa53b2f39815ae2f40ec9b74d809c0a","tid":537600,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T00:10:10.000Z","msg":"唔係嘛呢套Jumanji都得，不如上返第一集啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4979d38114ecc5fc503dabe2793bde5af3bb7119","tid":537600,"uid":1591